{"tid":481910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚諗住識下女姐 又遇到支那騙徒","createTime":"2017-11-27T15:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T01:05:21.000Z","uid":1925,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"730a3b1ac639e3212094b3ff3f60f10c4959bfac","tid":481910,"uid":1925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:21:22.000Z","msg":"話說前幾日上tinder掃下啲女<br />\n平時閪冧係度掃都match唔到一個<br />\n竟然又會比我match到個 心諗執撚到啦<br />\n即刻hi鳩佢啦 跟住佢就話佢係大陸落黎做陪酒<br />\n岩岩落黎冇人冇朋想識下朋友<br />\n仲問我介唔介意 心諗梗係無撚所謂啦 我都係純粹搵條女同我傾下計 黎填補下我寂莫的心姐 <br />\n跟住咪加撚左we柒囉(好日都唔撚開黎用)<br />\n我再睇下佢個交友圈又有啲好耐既post 又好多合照 咪當佢係真人先囉 <br />\n傾左一晚都正正常常 又話帶佢香港周圍玩果啲<br />\n到岩岩 佢就講話個佢個老細要佢去接個客 係要性服務<br />\n佢話唔想接要我幫佢喎 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/225410_5296cbe840e5e4d7f3c401ea717eb998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F225410_5296cbe840e5e4d7f3c401ea717eb998.jpg&h=f84e0cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/225506_142bee1bc54141e7f62a5ab9f001dba1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F225506_142bee1bc54141e7f62a5ab9f001dba1.jpg&h=1ef398d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/225507_8189a3b358bfdd6d4c8269de88fbaf5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F225507_8189a3b358bfdd6d4c8269de88fbaf5a.jpg&h=16ac95ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/225508_0070c3334360e8ab99403556e6674579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F225508_0070c3334360e8ab99403556e6674579.jpg&h=12d2482e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/225510_62f0683f58a33624bb5ae0043a9197a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F225510_62f0683f58a33624bb5ae0043a9197a8.jpg&h=ac2e56b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/225511_c34a927f6fb604460cb18581047dd3df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F225511_c34a927f6fb604460cb18581047dd3df.jpg&h=5f27adcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身都諗唔到咩騙案住既，心諗要幫既咪你唔好撈拎囇啲野黎我屋企接濟住你先囉 <br />\n令我開始覺得奇撚怪既係我問佢啲野又唔答，一味就係話要我用佢個方法：拎錢出黎扮約佢，從而避左個客，之後再還比我。一講撚到錢，即刻醒爬啦屌。愈諗愈唔對路啦，個心繼而又up左下。心諗唉，屌你老母，難得有條女同我傾左咁耐，原來又係呃錢既唉屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/231026_8ce7de6408aabc5a9a6ead61d6739701.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F231026_8ce7de6408aabc5a9a6ead61d6739701.jpg&h=aa0f2610&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/231027_fa8593a359f7a78eb3eb0f8795d87494.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F231027_fa8593a359f7a78eb3eb0f8795d87494.jpg&h=e0400bd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/231028_3c96bf437fc6a9bfc1822cb2336c46f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F231028_3c96bf437fc6a9bfc1822cb2336c46f9.jpg&h=111b0668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n果啲乜乜美容雞，買點數盛果啲就聽得多<br />\n呢個我真係第一次見。騙徒手法真係層出不窮架<br />\n支那人真係十居其九都係賊黎架你老母<br />\n想提醒大家真係小心，呢個case我都算少聽"},{"pid":"e8348bac86e8f69f81338b38334be08825785e20","tid":481910,"uid":106093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"隔離有佳佳都中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aed0a05372c896324352edcf3ddab3aeba30777","tid":481910,"uid":1925,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隔離有佳佳都中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c